    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Worsening pain around bowel movement, with decreased pain post rectal evacuation\nPerirectal abscesses often accompanied by\nfever\n,\nleukocytosis\nMay only be palpable via digital rectal exam\nPerianal abscesses typically do not cause fever in immunocompetent individuals\nTender inguinal\nlymphadenopathy\nmay be only clue to deeper abscesses",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
